{"data":{"page":{"id":"e6bbdea8-67e1-5621-9c8c-d7a504806cbc","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://tensionstudio.com\" target=\"_blank\">Launch website</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"0\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9c6e6cb3c7b56a90006a6eeb64618c67/6b333/0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9c6e6cb3c7b56a90006a6eeb64618c67/f3ce7/0.jpg 200w,\n/static/9c6e6cb3c7b56a90006a6eeb64618c67/72342/0.jpg 400w,\n/static/9c6e6cb3c7b56a90006a6eeb64618c67/6b333/0.jpg 800w,\n/static/9c6e6cb3c7b56a90006a6eeb64618c67/40247/0.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>I met Josep Manen in 2002 and since then, we have partnered in many cultural and artistic projects. He’s a very talented musician, specialiasing in sound engineering for multimedia productions and his website features his services and the projects he has created.</p>\n<p>Josep asked me to build a Wordpress website for his brand: Tension Studio. A few months later, we created a new template with an e-commerce module.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 624px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 41.826923